AssetManager for loading/saving scenes locally and remotely. GDResponse and status codes for handling response state. Updated scene and GDP serialization
Fixed crash of deleting serialized component. Added WizardSamples project for unit testing of WizardEngine details. SceneService for dispatching and processing scene requests on server side.

Project Template System, replaced GLM library with my own Math System.
Initial work to fix visual bug with matrices.
Fixed visual 3D projection issue, caused by incorrect matrix multiplication order. Changed order (projection * view) into (view * projection).
Fixed visual 3D projection issue, caused by incorrect matrix multiplication order. Changed order (projection * view) into (view * projection).
Ray Casting, Advanced Camera, refactored EventRegistry, can't add more than 1 color attachment to scene FBO.
Fixed mouse cursor update position, when moving, zooming and rotating camera.
Material System, Phong, SolidPhong, Mouse Picking, Ray Cast, updated EventRegistry, updated Math functions, little updates in Renderers, updated Light System
Fixed TextureBuffer::load, TextureBuffer creation functions.

Material System, refactored Render System, HDR/LDR, blinn-phong lighting, diffuse map, specular map, normal map, parallax map, gamma correction, making Batching/Instancing render faster. Fixed a lot of crash and memory issues with Render System.

Post Effects Rendering, MRT support, a couple of refactoring of Shader API and Render API. Added next post effects : HDR/LDR, Blur, Edge Detection, Sharpen, Gaussian Blur. Added TextureMixer as a renderer that receives texture id list as an input, mixes all textures inside pixel shader and outputs it in separate frame buffer texture attachment. Added ImGui as Visual support, if macro VISUAL is defined inside the app you are building. This system has different widgets, console, themes. Added primitive vertex shader that allows to draw geometry without using VBO, VAO, IBO.

Basic Physics, simulation of objects velocity, collision detection for SphereCollider, AABBCollider, PlaneCollider, callbacks and respond to detected/undetected collision. When objects are collided, they will be reflected into different direction based on direction they had during simulation.
Custom Profiler, GPU Debugger, few more Visuals, support of Gizmos UI with ImGuizmo, Timer, TextureArray
Moving WizardEngine into DLL library, fixing all conflicts after DLL migration, added RCC++, naming and convention changes.

More features for Project Managment System. Updated Asset Managment and Scene systems. Added visual Logger and other visual tools for editor. Changed theme for WizardStudio Changed AssetBrowser for WizardStudio. Added Runtime Compile/Build/Run system. Added Runtime Build Zipping feature for game distribution.
